summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 227E, page 18, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in University Lake Shore Park, Lots 45 to 47, inclusive, Block 1, located on the southwest corner of 35th Ave. N.E. and E. 125th St. as Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
